# Frontend Rules

## Stack

- React 19, TypeScript strict, Vite 6 (HTTPS dev server)
- MUI 7 for UI primitives; TailwindCSS 4 for custom styling; Emotion for component CSS-in-JS
- React Router 7 — routes under `@pages`

## Imports

Use path aliases, not deep relative paths: `@components`, `@pages`, `@services`, `@ui`, `@hooks`, `@contexts`, `@utils`

## UI requirements

- **Dark mode**: use MUI `useTheme()` — no hardcoded colors
- **i18n**: all user-facing strings through localization (`LangContext` / existing i18n) — no hardcoded Arabic or English
- **Responsive**: mobile 320px, tablet 768px, desktop 1280px+ — MUI Grid/Container + Tailwind breakpoints

## Auth & data

- Auth via `keycloak-js`; guard routes with `ProtectedRoute` and `RoleGuard`
- Tables: prefer `@mui/x-data-grid`
- Add `data-testid` on interactive elements (no test framework yet, but code must be testable)
